#: ../../source/architecture.rst:2
msgid "Architecture Overview"
msgstr "架构概述"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:4
msgid ""
"Fabricatio is a Python LLM application framework built with an event-"
"driven, multi-agent architecture. It leverages Rust (via PyO3) for "
"performance-critical components, Handlebars for templating, and async "
"Python for workflow orchestration."
msgstr ""
"Fabricatio 是一个基于事件驱动、多智能体架构构建的 Python LLM 应用框架。它利用 Rust（通过 PyO3）实现性能关键组件，使用 Handlebars "
"进行模板渲染，并采用异步 Python 进行工作流编排。"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:7
msgid "Event-Driven Agent Architecture"
msgstr "事件驱动的智能体架构"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:9
msgid ""
"At its core, Fabricatio implements an event-driven agent pattern where "
"roles respond to events through registered skills that map to workflow "
"sequences:"
msgstr ""
"Fabricatio 的核心实现了事件驱动的智能体模式，其中角色通过已注册的技能响应事件，这些技能映射到工作流序列："

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:31
msgid "Core Concepts"
msgstr "核心概念"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:33
msgid "**Role**"
msgstr "**Role（角色）**"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:34
msgid ""
"The primary agent entity. A Role wraps a set of Skills and provides the "
"interface for task delegation and LLM interaction."
msgstr ""
"主要的智能体实体。Role 封装了一组 Skill，并提供任务委派和 LLM 交互的接口。"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:36
msgid "**Event**"
msgstr "**Event（事件）**"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:37
msgid ""
"A trigger mechanism using ``EventEmitter`` pattern. Events are identified"
" by name and can be quickly instantiated via "
"``Event.quick_instantiate()``."
msgstr ""
"一种使用 ``EventEmitter`` 模式的触发机制。事件通过名称标识，可通过 "
"``Event.quick_instantiate()`` 快速实例化。"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:39
msgid "**Skill**"
msgstr "**Skill（技能）**"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:40
msgid ""
"A named capability that maps an Event to a WorkFlow. Skills are stored in"
" a Role's skill registry."
msgstr ""
"一种将 Event 映射到 WorkFlow 的命名能力。Skill 存储在 Role 的技能注册表中。"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:42
msgid "**WorkFlow**"
msgstr "**WorkFlow（工作流）**"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:43
msgid ""
"A sequence of Actions to execute. WorkFlows can be synchronous (blocking)"
" or asynchronous."
msgstr ""
"要执行的 Action 序列。WorkFlow 可以是同步（阻塞）的或异步的。"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:45
msgid "**Task**"
msgstr "**Task（任务）**"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:46
msgid ""
"A unit of work assigned to a Role. Tasks carry input data and can be "
"delegated to registered Skills."
msgstr ""
"分配给 Role 的工作单元。Task 携带输入数据，可委派给已注册的 Skill。"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:48
msgid "**Action**"
msgstr "**Action（动作）**"

#: ../../source/architecture.rst:49
msgid ""
"The atomic execution unit. Actions implement the actual logic and can "
"access LLM capabilities through mixins."
msgstr ""
"原子执行单元。Action 实现实际逻辑，并可通过 mixin 访问 LLM 能力。"

